                            <comment id="13102939" author="dkulp" created="Mon, 12 Sep 2011 19:19:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oli,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How easy is it for you to reproduce and test this?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I just discovered the call in JAXBContextCache to &quot;remove&quot; was not in a synchronized block which could definitely cause this.   I&apos;m committing that fix to trunk and the branches, but would definitely like to see this tested to make sure it really fixes the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
